{"tid":806472,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)永安改機票一問","createTime":"2018-09-04T16:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T04:36:49.000Z","uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd2584861a94081869d8f866e27b87c9012bf8f","tid":806472,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:39:45.000Z","msg":"我買左英國去香港既cx回程機票<br />\n時間係下星期<br />\n經skyscanner 係永安旅遊買<br />\n佢地無出cx既 booking reference <br />\n只係有ticket confirmation <br />\n上面有ticket confirmation number <br />\nWing on booking ID<br />\n<br />\n不過我依加有急事想改早一兩日<br />\n我send左email去永安<br />\n但係我相信佢地唔要email<br />\n但我人在外地 打唔到電話返香港<br />\n亦無人係香港可以幫手<br />\n請問有冇巴打絲打們試過要喺永安改機票<br />\n請問點樣先可以改到機票<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢re routing conditions<br />\nBefore departure 1532$HKD + 90$CNY<br />\n咁呢個係咪就一定係改機票價錢？<br />\n同埋有冇人知道最遲係幾時改？<br />\n<br />\n跪求巴絲打比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aee9caa918a52a61198abd93a8a44c1cfb53900","tid":806472,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"一定要經agent 改 直接打電話問喇"},{"pid":"33af638bd633cf3f52f92a7aa4e9ceb5a5ef2863","tid":806472,"uid":198622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:11:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"303945051c0750454a215966420da03c9d02fe1a","tid":806472,"uid":198622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:13:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65fcd40b5699c4077b5ca5b507f3495aac8a94e8","tid":806472,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aee9caa918a52a61198abd93a8a44c1cfb53900","tid":806472,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"一定要經agent 改 直接打電話問喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:23:30.000Z","msg":"英國電話打唔返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de74e8a9cd2cb1a9a75dbe9602b7ee5b093